description: The man and woman have been sentenced after the first FGM conviction in the Republic of Ireland.
title: FGM: Dublin couple jailed over genital mutilation of daughter

maintext: He concluded her injury could not have been accidental when he performed a procedure to stop her bleeding and referred the case to the Garda (Irish police) for investigation.
